name: ˟_0xThxxghtx1˟thathumanfeeling...˟˟
description:
That human feeling of seeking calm, that unconscious need to stop and simply do nothing waiting for death materializes in order, in simply accepting that chaos is there but wanting to deny it by seeking calm, seeking not to understand and only feel that he understands, seeking not to over analyze and only feel comfortable with what he sees without going beyond or bothering with anything?
But that is not necessarily a problem, the point of view is important, the point of view is the one that can turn all the above into a simple writing made by someone who does not believe in life, or can turn it into a law, always the point of view will govern the real meaning of things, you can not impose your belief nor can you simply close yourself to a point of view, that is one more form of calm....
